name: Cognex.cmbSDK
summary: The Cognex Mobile Barcode SDK to read barcodes with your mobile device.
description:
The Cognex Mobile Barcode SDK supports all major barcode symbologies, including Aztec Code, Codabar, Code 11, Code 25 (Interleaved,
Industrial and ITF-14), Code 39, Code 93, Code 128, Data Matrix, DotCode, EAN, ISBN, GS1 Databar, MaxiCode, MSI Plessey, PDF417, 
Postal Code, QR Code (Micro and Standard), TELEPEN and UPC barcode types, as well as all GS1 specific sub types like GS1 QR Code, 
GS1 DataMatrix and GS1-128.
You can add powerful parser plugins to the Cognex Mobile Barcode SDK at no additional cost when you purchase an SDK license or 
hardware accessory. Plugins include industry standard parsers such as AAMVA, GS1, IUID, Structured Carrier Messages, and more!
